	ascade Motorcycle Safety and Ride With Us for a chance to experience ridin
	g a motorcycle for free\\\, with professional Cascade Motorcycle Safety Ri
	derCoaches helping you through each step. These 1-on-1\\\, 20-minute sessi
	ons are designed for total beginners\\\, with bikes and helmets provided. 
	\\nThis program is presented with the support of Cascade Motorcycle Safety
	. \\nRide out the remainder of the day in MOHAI to see Kickstands Up! 125 
	Years of Motorcycling in the PNW. Program participants will receive a coup
	on for $5 off museum admission. \\nAs of 2/18/26\\\, the location and time
	 of this event has changed.\n\nhttps://mohai.org/event/motorcycle-riding-e
